+### Companion Mode: What It Is
+
+Instead of (or in addition to) material lookup, Drew acts as a **knowledgeable assistant** that helps users navigate the app and understand construction concepts.
+
+**Companion mode handles:**
+- "How do I add a client?"
+- "How do I generate a PDF?"
+- "What's the difference between labor and overhead?"
+- "How do I share a quote with a customer?"
+- "What's markup vs margin?"
+- "How do I duplicate a quote?"
+- "Where are my invoices?"
+
+**Benefits:**
+- **Much simpler** - Just needs app knowledge, no product catalog integration
+- **Lower risk** - Wrong answer about navigation doesn't lose a sale
+- **Immediately useful** - Helps onboarding and feature discovery
+- **Works reliably** - No external API dependencies
+- **Ships fast** - Could implement in a day
+
